name: Phytoplankton data collected during cruises on the R/V Knipovich in 1948 and 1950
description: Phytoplankton data collected by the IBSS staff on theR/VKnipovich in the BlackSea along the Yalta-Batumitransect during the cruise in August-September 1948, and along the Yalta - Sukhumi transect, diurnal station 8, 50 kmfrom Sukhumi in April 1950. This dataset contains abundancedata (individuals per liter) for phytoplankton taxa collected in layer anddiscrete depths samples. Biomass data (mg/mÂ³) are also available for 1948. No additionalmetadata is available.
